    "Normalization is essential for ensuring that the various features are on a similar scale and that one does not dominate the others during the modeling process.",
    "This step enhances the model's stability and performance.",
    "Following normalization, we transformed the features into a numpy array, a data structure ideal for numerical computations and analysis.",
    "When working with data, Numpy arrays provide efficiency and flexibility.",
    "Following that, we reshaped the data to meet the needs of our chosen machine-learning models."
